Title: The New Boss
Plot: A new editor is picked up at Full Steam Magazine, and the boys all do their best to impress. Gibbs' game gets shaky, Neal experiences a colossal confidence boost and Milo tries to get noticed. Meanwhile, Tyler tries to change up his dating style, and it doesn't go quite as well as he'd like to think.
ParentalRatingReason: Lightbox Provisional Classification. Official NZ Rating To Be Confirmed.
GuestStars: Peri Gilpin, J.K. Simmons, Joel David Moore, John Michael Higgins, Hannah Duncan, Melissa Fumero, Karl Michael Maschek, Tim Scanlon
